    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>Up to three creatures of your choice that you can see within range must make Charisma saving throws. Whenever a target that fails this saving throw makes an attack roll or a saving throw before the spell ends, the target must roll a [[/r d4]] and subtract the number rolled from the attack roll or saving throw.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p></p><div data-roll-name-ancestor=\"At Higher Levels\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"1\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">At Higher Levels.</span></span> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, you can target one additional creature for each slot level above 1st.</p></div></div>",
